    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> toasted sesame oil</strong>,<strong> mirin</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>miso paste</strong>, <strong>ginger paste</strong> and <strong>soy sauce </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Add 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and mix well – this is your <strong>miso sauce</strong></p><p>Once the green beans have started to soften, add the <strong>miso sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until it begins to simmer</p>",
      "order": 4,
